data.description: Welcome Home! Centrally located and affordably priced, 3-level condo in Clover Creek Condominiums in Lakewood. Spacious floor plan, light and bright living room and kitchen on the 2nd level, bonus room/rec room on the main, 2 bedrooms and utility room on the 3rd level. One full bath, one 3/4 bath and one half bath. 1 car attached garage, conveniently located to all amenities and more. End unit with 2nd level balcony.  HOA no longer active, no HOA dues.
